    Options Indexes Includes MultiViews
    Order allow,deny
    Allow from all

    AuthUserFile /opt/hobbit/server/etc/hobbitpasswd
    AuthType Basic
    AuthName &#x26;quot;Security&#x26;quot;
    Require user unixadmins devteam
&#x26;lt;/Directory&#x26;gt;

&#x26;lt;Directory &#x26;quot;/opt/hobbit/server/www/menu&#x26;quot;&#x26;gt;
    Options Indexes Includes MultiViews
    Order allow,deny
    Allow from all

    AuthUserFile /opt/hobbit/server/etc/hobbitpasswd
    AuthType Basic
